{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Impose new restrictions on the placement mobile speed cameras",
        "additional_details": "We believe it is unfair that mobile speed cameras can be situated on verges or other areas where cars cannot legally parked, and on ascents or descents, that can impact the speed of a vehicle.",
        "background": "We want the Government to restrict the placement of mobile speed cameras so they can only be located in places that are legally parking spaces, and on flat stretches of road.",
